<h2 id="working-in-the-open">Working in the open</h2>
<p>The community backlog lives in the open using project boards on GitHub .</p>
<p>Project boards on GitHub are <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanban_board">Kanban boards</a>. They help organise and prioritise the community backlog. We have 3 project boards:</p>

<ul class="nhsuk-list">
